profile:
Magnolia Construction prides itself on the ability to listen and anticipate wants and needs. That’s what makes us exceptional at customizing our services to the unique situation of each and every client. We guide your vision through the entire renovation process and ensure that we are on the same page as to the best way to achieve it.

Our team of designers and builders brings expertise in a wide variety of aspects in home remodelling, and our track record of customer satisfaction earns us repeat business and referrals. You’ll find us as attentive and courteous in customer service as in the remodelling work itself.

We’ve transformed many a kitchen in Ottawa, with renovations ranging from islands and new counter tops to knocking down walls and changing the entire dynamic to a more contemporary space. Our extensive experience in kitchen renovations means you’re getting highly skilled craftsmanship to execute an exquisite transformation. Our clients give us rave reviews and have great things to say about the renovations we’ve done for the kitchens and other living spaces.

Our bathroom renovations deliver quality results, on time and on budget. We’ll work with you to create an upgraded bathroom that makes you want to linger for a while, light a candle and relax. We’ve remodeled countless bathrooms in Ottawa homes, from counters and sinks to showers & tubs to tile floors. We leave no stone unturned when we executive a renovation, keeping your full satisfaction in mind at every measurement, cut and fitting.

Magnolia will transform your basement from “blah” to “wow.” We’ll work with you to design and deliver a functional, livable basement space that your family (or your tenant) will truly enjoy. We have a knack for translating visions into reality. Talk to Magnolia about how we can work together to build a dream basement. When it comes to basements there’s no need to aim low. You deserve the best quality renovation. Magnolia can make that happen.
services: Bathroom renovations, kitchen renovations, basement renovations, additions, general contracting, landscaping, decks
name: Magnolia Construction

profile:
A design-build, construction project management and renovation firm, Sierra Gate Homes has twenty-five years of experience in residential construction.  We are a licensed and registered builder with Tarion, and a member of the Greater Ottawa Home Builders' Association.  

At Sierra Gate Homes, we take great pride in the quality of our workmanship.  Our involvement, our suppliers and our trades set us apart from the competition.  Our clients receive hands-on customer service from the owner of the company.  And our commitment to our clients does not end upon completion of their project.  We stand behind the work we do.  This means that you can expect courteous and professional ongoing service from Sierra Gate Homes.
products:
Custom Conventional Homes

Sierra Gate Homes builds custom conventional homes on lots owned by our clients.  

Lindal Cedar Homes

Sierra Gate Homes is proud to be the independent Lindal Cedar Homes representative for Eastern Ontario.  Lindal is the first and largest manufacturer of cedar custom homes in the world.  Whether you are looking for a cozy cottage retreat, a permanent home that fits your growing family’s lifestyle, or a relaxing retirement home, we will work with you to achieve your dream.  When you purchase a Lindal home, you are not only buying the highest quality materials in the industry backed by a lifetime structural warranty, you are rewarding yourself with the Lindal experience.  The Lindal family heritage is built on over 65 years of planning, designing and building dream homes for more than 55,000 clients worldwide.
services:
Design-Build

The process starts and ends with you.  In your first meeting with Sierra Gate Homes, you describe your project in detail.  We listen carefully to your ideas and develop a clear understanding of your lifestyle needs.  Using the information that you provide to us, we design and build a home that meets or surpasses your expectations.  As a design-build firm, Sierra Gate Homes provides you with a comprehensive range of design and construction services.  We work with you from project conception until the final inspection of your home.  

Construction Project Management

As a construction project management firm, Sierra Gate Homes manages the entire construction process on your behalf and ensures that it flows smoothly.  Our expertise allows us to attend to all project details and minimise costs.  We work with you from the design phase until the final inspection of your home. 

Renovations and Additions 

Sierra Gate Homes works closely with you to ensure that your project makes your vision a reality, and that it is completed efficiently, on time and on budget.  We apply the same high standards to our renovations and additions that we bring to our custom home projects.  Our trades are highly skilled and committed to excellence.  They take great pride in providing premier quality workmanship.
memberships: Tarion, Greater Ottawa Home Builders' Association
name: Sierra Gate Homes

profile: Founded by Wes Nicol in 1966, Tartan rapidly became an Ottawa leader in community development and home construction. The company’s first projects, The Faircrest and The Highlands, are still regarded as the region’s most successful apartment dwelling developments. It was followed by the company’s leadership in turning Barrhaven into one of the region’s most popular family communities. The company also undertook prestigious developments in Florida, while continuing to build homes – and a stellar reputation – here at home. Today, Tartan is under the direction of the next generation of Nicols, Wes’ sons Ian and Bruce. And it is more active building superior homes and developing popular communities than at any time in its history.
name: Tartan Homes Corp
